  "title": "Structure",
  "content": "<!-- wp:greenshift-blocks/element {\"id\":\"gsbp-0001449\",\"tag\":\"section\",\"type\":\"inner\",\"localId\":\"gsbp-0001449\",\"align\":\"full\",\"dynamicAttributes\":[{\"name\":\"data-type\",\"value\":\"section-component\"}],\"styleAttributes\":{\"display\":[\"flex\"],\"justifyContent\":[\"center\"],\"flexDirection\":[\"column\"],\"alignItems\":[\"center\"],\"paddingRight\":[\"var(\\u002d\\u002dwp\\u002d\\u002dcustom\\u002d\\u002dspacing\\u002d\\u002dside, min(3vw, 20px))\"],\"paddingLeft\":[\"var(\\u002d\\u002dwp\\u002d\\u002dcustom\\u002d\\u002dspacing\\u002d\\u002dside, min(3vw, 20px))\"],\"paddingTop\":[\"var(\\u002d\\u002dwp\\u002d\\u002dcustom\\u002d\\u002dspacing\\u002d\\u002dtop, 0px)\"],\"paddingBottom\":[\"var(\\u002d\\u002dwp\\u002d\\u002dcustom\\u002d\\u002dspacing\\u002d\\u002dbottom, 0px)\"],\"marginTop\":[\"0px\"],\"marginBottom\":[\"0px\"],\"paddingLink_Extra\":\"lr\",\"position\":[\"relative\"],\"backgroundColor\":[\"var(\\u002d\\u002dwp\\u002d\\u002dpreset\\u002d\\u002dcolor\\u002d\\u002dcard-border, #f0f0f0)\"]},\"isVariation\":\"contentwrapper\"} -->\n<section class=\"gsbp-0001449 alignfull\" data-type=\"section-component\"><!-- wp:greenshift-blocks/element {\"id\":\"gsbp-edbf021\",\"type\":\"inner\",\"localId\":\"gsbp-edbf021\",\"styleAttributes\":{\"marginTop\":[\"48px\"],\"marginBottom\":[\"48px\"],\"marginLeft\":[\"0px\"],\"marginRight\":[\"0px\"],\"paddingLink_Extra\":\"all\",\"paddingTop\":[\"0px\"],\"paddingBottom\":[\"0px\"],\"paddingLeft\":[\"0px\"],\"paddingRight\":[\"0px\"],\"marginLink_Extra\":\"tb\"}} -->\n<div class=\"gsbp-edbf021\"><!-- wp:greenshift-blocks/element {\"id\":\"gsbp-7555071\",\"textContent\":\"រចនាសម្ព័ន្ធក្រសួង\",\"tag\":\"h2\",\"localId\":\"gsbp-7555071\",\"styleAttributes\":{\"marginLink_Extra\":\"all\",\"marginTop\":[\"0\"],\"marginBottom\":[\"0\"],\"marginLeft\":[\"0\"],\"marginRight\":[\"0\"]}} -->\n<h2 class=\"gsbp-7555071\">រចនាសម្ព័ន្ធក្រសួង</h2>\n<!-- /wp:greenshift-blocks/element --></div>\n<!-- /wp:greenshift-blocks/element -->\n\n<!-- wp:greenshift-blocks/element {\"id\":\"gsbp-e08ed10\",\"metadata\":{\"name\":\"Content Area\"},\"type\":\"inner\",\"localId\":\"gsbp-e08ed10\",\"dynamicAttributes\":[{\"name\":\"data-type\",\"value\":\"content-area-component\"}],\"styleAttributes\":{\"maxWidth\":[\"100%\"],\"width\":[\"var(\\u002d\\u002dwp\\u002d\\u002dstyle\\u002d\\u002dglobal\\u002d\\u002dwide-size, 1200px)\"],\"backgroundColor\":[\"var(\\u002d\\u002dwp\\u002d\\u002dpreset\\u002d\\u002dcolor\\u002d\\u002dcontrastcolor, #fffffe)\"],\"marginTop\":[\"\"],\"marginBottom\":[\"48px\"],\"borderRadiusLink_Extra\":true,\"borderTopLeftRadius\":[\"7px\"],\"borderBottomLeftRadius\":[\"7px\"],\"borderTopRightRadius\":[\"7px\"],\"borderBottomRightRadius\":[\"7px\"],\"paddingTop\":[\"24px\"],\"paddingBottom\":[\"4em\"],\"paddingLeft\":[\"24px\"],\"paddingRight\":[\"24px\"],\"boxShadow\":[\"var(\\u002d\\u002dwp\\u002d\\u002dpreset\\u002d\\u002dshadow\\u002d\\u002dsoft, 0px 15px 30px 0px rgba(119, 123, 146, 0.1))\"]},\"isVariation\":\"nocolumncontent\"} -->\n<div class=\"gsbp-e08ed10\" data-type=\"content-area-component\"><!-- wp:greenshift-blocks/element {\"id\":\"gsbp-e1eda41\",\"type\":\"inner\",\"localId\":\"gsbp-e1eda41\",\"styleAttributes\":{\"marginLink_Extra\":\"all\",\"marginTop\":[\"0px\"],\"marginBottom\":[\"0px\"],\"marginLeft\":[\"0px\"],\"marginRight\":[\"0px\"],\"paddingLink_Extra\":\"all\",\"paddingTop\":[\"0px\"],\"paddingBottom\":[\"0px\"],\"paddingLeft\":[\"0px\"],\"paddingRight\":[\"0px\"],\"alignSelf\":[\"start\"],\"justifySelf\":[\"start\"]}} -->\n<div class=\"gsbp-e1eda41\"><!-- wp:greenshift-blocks/element {\"id\":\"gsbp-5fa756b\",\"textContent\":\"យោងតាមអនុក្រឹត្យលេខ \\u003ca href=\\u0022https://mptc.gov.kh/?p=30154\\u0022 target=\\u0022_blank\\u0022 rel=\\u0022noreferrer noopener\\u0022\\u003e៦៤ អនក្រ.បក\\u003c/a\\u003e ចុះថ្ងៃទី១០ ខែឧសភា ឆ្នាំ២០១៩ ស្តីពីការរៀបចំ និងការប្រព្រឹត្តទៅ នៃក្រសួងប្រៃសណីយ៍និងទូរគមនាគមន៍ និងអនុក្រឹត្យលេខ \\u003ca href=\\u0022https://mptc.gov.kh/%e1%9e%9a%e1%9e%85%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%9f%e1%9e%98%e1%9f%92%e1%9e%96%e1%9f%90%e1%9e%93%e1%9f%92%e1%9e%92%e1%9e%80%e1%9f%92%e1%9e%9a%e1%9e%9f%e1%9e%bd%e1%9e%84/\\u0022 target=\\u0022_blank\\u0022 rel=\\u0022noreferrer noopener\\u0022\\u003e២២៧ អនក្រ.បក\\u003c/a\\u003e ស្តីពីការរៀបចំ និងប្រព្រឹត្តទៅនៃបណ្ឌិតសភាបច្ចេកវិទ្យាឌីជីថលកម្ពុជា រចនាសម្ព័ន្ធក្រសួងត្រូវបានកំណត់ដោយអង្គការលេខខាងក្រោមនេះ៖\",\"tag\":\"p\",\"localId\":\"gsbp-5fa756b\",\"styleAttributes\":{\"alignSelf\":[\"center\"],\"justifySelf\":[\"center\"],\"color\":[\"#3b3b3b\"],\"marginTop\":[\"15px\"],\"marginBottom\":[\"0px\"],\"marginLeft\":[\"0px\"],\"marginRight\":[\"0px\"],\"fontSize\":[\"16px\"]}} -->\n<p class=\"gsbp-5fa756b\">យោងតាមអនុក្រឹត្យលេខ <a href=\"https://mptc.gov.kh/?p=30154\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">៦៤ អនក្រ.បក</a> ចុះថ្ងៃទី១០ ខែឧសភា ឆ្នាំ២០១៩ ស្តីពីការរៀបចំ និងការប្រព្រឹត្តទៅ នៃក្រសួងប្រៃសណីយ៍និងទូរគមនាគមន៍ និងអនុក្រឹត្យលេខ <a href=\"https://mptc.gov.kh/%e1%9e%9a%e1%9e%85%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%9f%e1%9e%98%e1%9f%92%e1%9e%96%e1%9f%90%e1%9e%93%e1%9f%92%e1%9e%92%e1%9e%80%e1%9f%92%e1%9e%9a%e1%9e%9f%e1%9e%bd%e1%9e%84/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">២២៧ អនក្រ.បក</a> ស្តីពីការរៀបចំ និងប្រព្រឹត្តទៅនៃបណ្ឌិតសភាបច្ចេកវិទ្យាឌីជីថលកម្ពុជា រចនាសម្ព័ន្ធក្រសួងត្រូវបានកំណត់ដោយអង្គការលេខខាងក្រោមនេះ៖</p>\n<!-- /wp:greenshift-blocks/element -->\n\n<!-- wp:greenshift-blocks/element {\"id\":\"gsbp-cbbb27b\",\"type\":\"inner\",\"localId\":\"gsbp-cbbb27b\",\"styleAttributes\":{\"justifySelf\":[\"center\"],\"marginTop\":[\"24px\"],\"textAlign\":[\"center\"]}} -->\n<div class=\"gsbp-cbbb27b\"><!-- wp:greenshift-blocks/element {\"id\":\"gsbp-9b7951e\",\"tag\":\"img\",\"className\":\"gsbp-9b7951e\",\"localId\":\"gsbp-9b7951e\",\"src\":\"http://dasiy.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/0fFBZ9f7-Structure_MPTC_V2_Page_1-2048x1450-1.jpg\",\"alt\":\"\",\"mediaid\":1648,\"originalWidth\":2048,\"originalHeight\":1450} -->\n<img class=\"gsbp-9b7951e\" src=\"http://dasiy.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/0fFBZ9f7-Structure_MPTC_V2_Page_1-2048x1450-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1450\" loading=\"lazy\"/>\n<!-- /wp:greenshift-blocks/element -->\n\n<!-- wp:greenshift-blocks/element {\"id\":\"gsbp-08d5ec0\",\"textContent\":\"ទាញយករចនាសម្ព័ន្ធ\",\"tag\":\"a\",\"dynamictext\":{\"dynamicEnable\":false},\"dynamiclink\":{\"dynamicEnable\":false},\"localId\":\"gsbp-08d5ec0\",\"href\":\"http://dasiy.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/Structure_MPTC_V2.pdf\",\"linkNewWindow\":true,\"linkNoFollow\":true,\"linkSponsored\":true,\"styleAttributes\":{\"alignSelf\":[\"\"],\"justifySelf\":[\"center\"],\"color\":[\"#004282\"],\"marginTop\":[\"15px\"],\"marginBottom\":[\"0px\"],\"marginLeft\":[\"0px\"],\"marginRight\":[\"0px\"],\"fontSize\":[\"20px\"],\"color_hover\":[\"var(\\u002d\\u002dwp\\u002d\\u002dpreset\\u002d\\u002dcolor\\u002d\\u002dsecondary, #f56c00)\"],\"textAlign\":[\"center\"],\"textDecoration\":[\"none\"]}} -->\n<a class=\"gsbp-08d5ec0\" href=\"http://dasiy.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/Structure_MPTC_V2.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow sponsored\">ទាញយករចនាសម្ព័ន្ធ</a>\n<!-- /wp:greenshift-blocks/element --></div>\n<!-- /wp:greenshift-blocks/element --></div>\n<!-- /wp:greenshift-blocks/element -->\n\n<!-- wp:greenshift-blocks/element {\"id\":\"gsbp-a59ef5c\",\"textContent\":\"​​ក្រសួង​ប្រៃសណីយ៍​ ​និង​ទូរគមនាគមន៍​ ​មាន​រចនា​ស​ម្ព័ន្ធ​ដូច​ខាងក្រោម​៖​\",\"tag\":\"p\",\"localId\":\"gsbp-a59ef5c\",\"styleAttributes\":{\"alignSelf\":[\"center\"],\"justifySelf\":[\"\"],\"color\":[\"#3b3b3b\"],\"marginTop\":[\"15px\"],\"marginBottom\":[\"0px\"],\"marginLeft\":[\"0px\"],\"marginRight\":[\"0px\"],\"fontSize\":[\"16px\"]}} -->\n<p class=\"gsbp-a59ef5c\">​​ក្រសួង​ប្រៃសណីយ៍​ ​និង​ទូរគមនាគមន៍​ ​មាន​រចនា​ស​ម្ព័ន្ធ​ដូច​ខាងក្រោម​៖​</p>\n<!-- /wp:greenshift-blocks/element -->\n\n<!-- wp:greenshift-blocks/element {\"id\":\"gsbp-e571c19\",\"type\":\"inner\",\"localId\":\"gsbp-e571c19\"} -->\n<div><!-- wp:greenshift-blocks/element {\"id\":\"gsbp-1127e53\",\"textContent\":\"\\u003cstrong\\u003eក​) ​អង្គភាព​ថ្នាក់​ជាតិ​\\u003c/strong\\u003e\",\"tag\":\"p\",\"localId\":\"gsbp-1127e53\",\"styleAttributes\":{\"alignSelf\":[\"center\"],\"justifySelf\":[\"\"],\"color\":[\"#3b3b3b\"],\"marginTop\":[\"15px\"],\"marginBottom\":[\"0px\"],\"marginLeft\":[\"0px\"],\"marginRight\":[\"0px\"],\"fontSize\":[\"18px\"]}} -->\n<p class=\"gsbp-1127e53\"><strong>ក​) ​អង្គភាព​ថ្នាក់​ជាតិ​</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:greenshift-blocks/element -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true,\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"16px\"}}} -->\n<ol style=\"font-size:16px\" class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>​ខុទ្ទកាល័យ​រដ្ឋមន្ត្រី​</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>​​អគ្គនាយកដ្ឋាន​<!-- wp:list {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"right\":\"20px\",\"left\":\"20px\"}}}} -->\n<ul style=\"padding-right:20px;padding-left:20px\" class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>​អគ្គនាយកដ្ឋាន​រដ្ឋបាល​</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>​អគ្គនាយកដ្ឋាន​ប្រៃសណីយ៍​</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>អគ្គនាយកដ្ឋាន​ទូរគមនាគមន៍​</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>​អគ្គនាយកដ្ឋាន​បច្ចេកវិទ្យា​គមនាគមន៍​ ​និង​ព័ត៌មាន​</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>​អគ្គនាយកដ្ឋាន​គ្រប់គ្រង​ធនធាន​វិសាលគម​ន៍ហ្វ្រេ​កង់​ស៍​វិទ្យុ​</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>​អគ្គាធិការ​ដ្ឋា​ន​​</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>នាយកដ្ឋាន​សវនកម្ម​ផ្ទៃក្នុង</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:greenshift-blocks/element -->\n\n<!-- wp:greenshift-blocks/element {\"id\":\"gsbp-18079ef\",\"type\":\"inner\",\"localId\":\"gsbp-18079ef\"} -->\n<div><!-- wp:greenshift-blocks/element {\"id\":\"gsbp-5a2d7c6\",\"textContent\":\"\\u003cstrong\\u003e\\u003cstrong\\u003eខ​) ​អង្គភាព​ស្វយ័ត​\\u003c/strong\\u003e\\u003c/strong\\u003e\",\"tag\":\"p\",\"localId\":\"gsbp-5a2d7c6\",\"styleAttributes\":{\"alignSelf\":[\"center\"],\"justifySelf\":[\"\"],\"color\":[\"#3b3b3b\"],\"marginTop\":[\"15px\"],\"marginBottom\":[\"0px\"],\"marginLeft\":[\"0px\"],\"marginRight\":[\"0px\"],\"fontSize\":[\"18px\"]}} -->\n<p class=\"gsbp-5a2d7c6\"><strong><strong>ខ​) ​អង្គភាព​ស្វយ័ត​</strong></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:greenshift-blocks/element -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true,\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"16px\"}}} -->\n<ol style=\"font-size:16px\" class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>និយ័ត​ករ​ទូរគមនាគមន៍​កម្ពុជា​</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>​សហគ្រាស​សាធារណៈ​<!-- wp:list {\"className\":\"is-style-default\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"right\":\"20px\",\"left\":\"20px\"}}}} -->\n<ul style=\"padding-right:20px;padding-left:20px\" class=\"wp-block-list is-style-default\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>ទូរគមនាគមន៍​កម្ពុជា​</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>​ប្រៃសណីយ៍​កម្ពុជា​</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>បណ្ឌិត្យសភាបច្ចេកវិទ្យាឌីជីថលកម្ពុជា</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:greenshift-blocks/element -->\n\n<!-- wp:greenshift-blocks/element {\"id\":\"gsbp-8762833\",\"type\":\"inner\",\"localId\":\"gsbp-8762833\"} -->\n<div><!-- wp:greenshift-blocks/element {\"id\":\"gsbp-b540b45\",\"textContent\":\"\\u003cstrong\\u003e\\u003cstrong\\u003e\\u003cstrong\\u003e​គ​) ​អង្គភាព​ថ្នាក់ក្រោម​ជាតិ\\u003c/strong\\u003e\\u003c/strong\\u003e\\u003c/strong\\u003e\",\"tag\":\"p\",\"localId\":\"gsbp-b540b45\",\"styleAttributes\":{\"alignSelf\":[\"center\"],\"justifySelf\":[\"\"],\"color\":[\"#3b3b3b\"],\"marginTop\":[\"15px\"],\"marginBottom\":[\"0px\"],\"marginLeft\":[\"0px\"],\"marginRight\":[\"0px\"],\"fontSize\":[\"18px\"]}} -->\n<p class=\"gsbp-b540b45\"><strong><strong><strong>​គ​) ​អង្គភាព​ថ្នាក់ក្រោម​ជាតិ</strong></strong></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:greenshift-blocks/element -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true,\"type\":\"decimal\",\"className\":\"is-style-default\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"16px\"},\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"right\":\"20px\",\"left\":\"20px\"}}}} -->\n<ol style=\"padding-right:20px;padding-left:20px;font-size:16px\" class=\"wp-block-list is-style-default\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>មន្ទីរប្រៃសណីយ៍​និង​ទូរគមនាគមន៍​ខេត្ត​</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:greenshift-blocks/element --></div>\n<!-- /wp:greenshift-blocks/element --></section>\n<!-- /wp:greenshift-blocks/element -->",
  "syncStatus": ""
}